channel.description: @johannes, I noticed that the Hirose Electric component ZX62D-B-5P8 is scheduled to be discontinued. Let me know if you want help with sustaining on this part. I'm working on an Autodesk Fusion 360 3D model of the Axoloti Core for use in designing cases / instruments and I noticed the discontinuation.
